| GAN Identities | Synthetic user count, % synthetic |
| Blockchain Ledger | Block count, recent blocks, chain validity |
| Canary Tokens | Trigger count by type |
| Behavioral Fingerprints | Attacker behavioral clusters |

**Live demo highlight:**
- Infrastructure Health drops from **17/17 → 16/17** when honeypot crashes during DDoS
- Returns to **17/17** when K8s watchdog restarts it — all visible in real time

