## SLIDE 16 — Testing & Validation

**Web Attack Testing (2_WEB_ATTACKS.sh):**
- 16 attacks simulated across all attack types
- Results: **16/16 detected, 100% detection rate**
- All malicious requests routed to honeypots — 0 reached real sites
- Average ML confidence: **93.2%**

**DDoS Testing (3_DDOS_ATTACK.sh):**
- 4-wave attack: Ramp-up → Sustained flood → Targeted kill → Slowloris
- Honeypot crash confirmed: port 4006 DOWN (verified by TCP check)
- Real site stays UP throughout (port 3006 unaffected)
- K8s auto-recovery: **honeypot restarted within ~15 seconds**
- Dashboard health: drops 16/17 then recovers 17/17

**Dashboard Metrics Verified:**
| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Total Attacks Logged | 216+ |
| Honeypot Events | 216+ (= Total Attacks) |
| Avg Detection Confidence | 93.2% |
| Detection Rate | 100% |
| Blockchain Blocks | 380+ (tamper-proof) |
| System Health | 17/17 |

