## SLIDE 20 — System Comparison: DeceptiCloud vs Traditional Security

**How DeceptiCloud Compares to Traditional Security**

| Feature | Firewall / IDS | DeceptiCloud |
|---------|---------------|-------------|
| Blocks attacks | ✅ | ✅ |
| Learns attacker techniques | ❌ | ✅ (behavioral fingerprinting) |
| Deceives attacker | ❌ | ✅ (LLM deception) |
| Evidence collection | Limited logs | ✅ Blockchain tamper-proof |
| Real-time monitoring | ✅ (basic) | ✅ Full SOC dashboard |
| Self-healing (K8s) | ❌ | ✅ Auto-recovery watchdog |
| AI-generated fake data | ❌ | ✅ GAN synthetic identities |
| Open-source & deployable | Varies | ✅ Docker-ready |

> *"Traditional security asks: 'Did we block it?' DeceptiCloud asks: 'What did we learn from it?'"*
